originalSql:
WITH RankedSuppliers AS (
    SELECT 
        s.s_suppkey,
        s.s_name,
        s.s_nationkey,
        s.s_acctbal,
        ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY s.s_nationkey ORDER BY s.s_acctbal DESC) AS Ran
    FROM 
        supplier s
),
SupplierRegion AS (
    SELECT 
        r.r_regionkey,
        r.r_name,
        n.n_name AS nation,
        s.s_suppkey,
        s.s_name
    FROM 
        region r
    JOIN 
        nation n ON r.r_regionkey = n.n_regionkey
    LEFT JOIN 
        RankedSuppliers s ON n.n_nationkey = s.s_nationkey
)
SELECT 
    p.p_name,
    SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS total_revenue,
    sr.nation,
    sr.r_name,
    COUNT(DISTINCT o.o_orderkey) AS order_count
FROM 
    part p
JOIN 
    lineitem l ON p.p_partkey = l.l_partkey
JOIN 
    orders o ON l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey
LEFT JOIN 
    SupplierRegion sr ON sr.s_suppkey = l.l_suppkey
WHERE 
    l.l_shipdate >= '1997-01-01' AND l.l_shipdate < '1997-12-31'
GROUP BY 
    p.p_name, sr.nation, sr.r_name
HAVING 
    SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) > (
        SELECT AVG(total_revenue)
        FROM (
            SELECT 
                SUM(l2.l_extendedprice * (1 - l2.l_discount)) AS total_revenue
            FROM 
                lineitem l2
            JOIN 
                orders o2 ON l2.l_orderkey = o2.o_orderkey
            WHERE 
                l2.l_shipdate >= '1997-01-01' AND l2.l_shipdate < '1997-12-31'
            GROUP BY 
                o2.o_orderkey
        ) AS order_totals
    )
ORDER BY 
    total_revenue DESC, p.p_name

FROM (SELECT AVG("t2"."TOTAL_REVENUE") AS "EXPR$0"
FROM (SELECT "orders"."o_orderkey", SUM("t0"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "t0"."l_discount")) AS "TOTAL_REVENUE"
FROM (SELECT *
FROM "lineitem"
WHERE "l_shipdate" >= DATE '1997-01-01' AND "l_shipdate" < DATE '1997-12-31') AS "t0"
INNER JOIN "orders" ON "t0"."l_orderkey" = "orders"."o_orderkey"
GROUP BY "orders"."o_orderkey") AS "t2") AS "t3"
INNER JOIN (SELECT "part"."p_name" AS "P_NAME", "t6"."NATION", "t6"."R_NAME", SUM("t4"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "t4"."l_discount")) AS "TOTAL_REVENUE", COUNT(DISTINCT "orders0"."o_orderkey") AS "ORDER_COUNT"
FROM "orders" AS "orders0"
INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "lineitem"
WHERE "l_shipdate" >= DATE '1997-01-01' AND "l_shipdate" < DATE '1997-12-31') AS "t4" INNER JOIN "part" ON "t4"."l_partkey" = "part"."p_partkey") ON "orders0"."o_orderkey" = "t4"."l_orderkey"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "region"."r_regionkey" AS "R_REGIONKEY", "region"."r_name" AS "R_NAME", "s1"."n_name" AS "NATION", "t5"."S_SUPPKEY", "t5"."S_NAME"
FROM (SELECT "s_suppkey" AS "S_SUPPKEY", "s_name" AS "S_NAME", "s_nationkey" AS "S_NATIONKEY", "s_acctbal" AS "S_ACCTBAL", ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY "s_nationkey" ORDER BY "s_acctbal" DESC NULLS FIRST) AS "RAN"
FROM "supplier") AS "t5"
RIGHT JOIN ("s1" INNER JOIN "region" ON "s1"."n_regionkey" = "region"."r_regionkey") ON "t5"."S_NATIONKEY" = "s1"."n_nationkey") AS "t6" ON "t4"."l_suppkey" = "t6"."S_SUPPKEY"
GROUP BY "part"."p_name", "t6"."NATION", "t6"."R_NAME") AS "t8" ON "t3"."EXPR$0" < "t8"."TOTAL_REVENUE"
ORDER BY "t8"."TOTAL_REVENUE" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t8"."P_NAME") AS "t10"

SELECT COALESCE("r_regionkey", "r_regionkey") AS "r_regionkey", "r_name", "r_comment"
FROM "region"

SELECT COALESCE("t10"."P_NAME", "t10"."P_NAME") AS "P_NAME", "t10"."TOTAL_REVENUE", "t10"."NATION", "t10"."R_NAME", "t10"."ORDER_COUNT", "t10"."p_name" AS "p_name_"
FROM (SELECT "t8"."P_NAME", "t8"."TOTAL_REVENUE", "t8"."NATION", "t8"."R_NAME", "t8"."ORDER_COUNT", "t8"."P_NAME" AS "p_name"
FROM (SELECT AVG("t2"."TOTAL_REVENUE") AS "EXPR$0"
FROM (SELECT "orders"."o_orderkey", SUM("t0"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "t0"."l_discount")) AS "TOTAL_REVENUE"
FROM (SELECT *
FROM "lineitem"
WHERE "l_shipdate" >= DATE '1997-01-01' AND "l_shipdate" < DATE '1997-12-31') AS "t0"
INNER JOIN "orders" ON "t0"."l_orderkey" = "orders"."o_orderkey"
GROUP BY "orders"."o_orderkey") AS "t2") AS "t3"
INNER JOIN (SELECT "part"."p_name" AS "P_NAME", "t6"."NATION", "t6"."R_NAME", SUM("t4"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "t4"."l_discount")) AS "TOTAL_REVENUE", COUNT(DISTINCT "orders0"."o_orderkey") AS "ORDER_COUNT"
FROM "orders" AS "orders0"
INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "lineitem"
WHERE "l_shipdate" >= DATE '1997-01-01' AND "l_shipdate" < DATE '1997-12-31') AS "t4" INNER JOIN "part" ON "t4"."l_partkey" = "part"."p_partkey") ON "orders0"."o_orderkey" = "t4"."l_orderkey"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "s1"."r_regionkey" AS "R_REGIONKEY", "s1"."r_name" AS "R_NAME", "nation"."n_name" AS "NATION", "t5"."S_SUPPKEY", "t5"."S_NAME"
FROM (SELECT "s_suppkey" AS "S_SUPPKEY", "s_name" AS "S_NAME", "s_nationkey" AS "S_NATIONKEY", "s_acctbal" AS "S_ACCTBAL", ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY "s_nationkey" ORDER BY "s_acctbal" DESC NULLS FIRST) AS "RAN"
FROM "supplier") AS "t5"
RIGHT JOIN ("nation" INNER JOIN "s1" ON "nation"."n_regionkey" = "s1"."r_regionkey") ON "t5"."S_NATIONKEY" = "nation"."n_nationkey") AS "t6" ON "t4"."l_suppkey" = "t6"."S_SUPPKEY"
GROUP BY "part"."p_name", "t6"."NATION", "t6"."R_NAME") AS "t8" ON "t3"."EXPR$0" < "t8"."TOTAL_REVENUE"
ORDER BY "t8"."TOTAL_REVENUE" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t8"."P_NAME") AS "t10"
